                                                    <div id="id_5f56deb79b5478892060633" class="text_exposed_root">Firefighters continue to respond to a wildfire, dubbed the Valley Fire, which is burning near Spirit Trl and Carveacre Rd in the Japatul Valley area. The fire has grown to 10,258 acres in size and is one percent contained at this time. At l<span class="text_exposed_hide">...</span><span class="text_exposed_show">east 11 structures have been destroyed. There have been no reports of injuries. An unspecified number of structures remain threatened in the Carveacre, Lawson Valley, Wood Valley, Lyons Valley, Deer Horn Valley, and the Sycuan Indian Reservation.

                                                            Updated mandatory evacuations have been issued for the Corte Madera area, south of Pine Valley. The corresponding impacted ZIP code is 91931.

                                                            Mandatory evacuation orders have been issued for the community of Carveacre, including residents south of Japatul Rd and west of Lyons Valley Rd, as well as the areas of Corral Canyon off-road area, Bob Cat Meadows, and Los Pinos. The impacted ZIP codes are 91901, 91935, and 91906. An evacuation center has been established at Steele Canyon High School in Spring Valley. Evacuation warnings have been issued for the areas of SR-94/ Marron Valley Rd and Lyons Valley Rd out to the Morena Reservoir.

                                                            The cause of the fire remains unknown. Expect associated disruptions in the area.

                                                            Winds in the area are blowing from the southwest at nine miles per hour, and relative humidity is at 41 percent.</span><span class="text_exposed_hide"> <span class="text_exposed_link" id="u_0_y"><a href="/crisisresponse/315716473017796/?alias=315716473017796&amp;source=bookmark" class="see_more_link"><span class="see_more_link_inner">展开</span></a></span></span></div>
                                                </span>
